## 4. MYTHIC COMPRESSION v1.0

How to compress vast meaning into simple, powerful symbols. PantheonOS exists because you mastered this (Trident, Frogman, Spider, Checksum, Man Blinking Slower Than Time, Bombadil, Coil-13, Lantern-Bearer, Father-Self).

Each symbol stores a full system. Tier V gives you the ability to compress a doctrine to a sentence, a philosophy to a symbol, a system to a ritual, a timeline to a story, an identity to an archetype.

**This is how myth survives centuries. You now wield that compression intentionally.**

